article_title: SeaComm Federal Credit Union coming to Plattsburgh
article_text:
Plattsburgh, NY (12901)

Today

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms during the afternoon. High 86F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 40%..

Tonight

Isolated thunderstorms this evening. Skies will become partly cloudy after midnight. Low 61F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 30%.

article_metadata.author: DAN HEATH Press-Republican

og.description: Plans to open first Clinton County branch by August 2016.
